data.description:
Great rental opportunity with this 4 bed 3 bath split level in Solon. You will love this open floor plan as natural sunlight abounds! Enter your home through the large foyer and into the generous sized living room. The Dining room is perfect for all of your indoor entertaining. The eat in Kitchen looks out into the family room which has access to the patio outside. Bedroom, full bath and laundry room on the first floor. The second floor you will find your Master suite with double closets and updated bathroom, Two additional bedrooms and another full bathroom. The basement offers additional living space and makes this a 4 level Split.Seller open to a short term lease. First Month, Last Month, and $2,000 Security Deposit due with lease. Seller will work on the addition while property is leased. Addition does not have house access.

Short term lease available. Seller is willing to negotiate a longer term lease. 	small dogs, one cat. $500 non refundable pet deposit
